Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um, Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a friend of Yanagi's, a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he used to work at a hospital in Obihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from ONLO?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagi asked me to help you with some counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was already here on business,\Nso I figured I might as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It is her. She's the one who shot Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fight me, and I'll make sure\Nyou get back unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hurt you. Just do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why be nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.67,0:00:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You shoot devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I only kill devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't kill humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But devils are human!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an advocate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that ambitious. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:00:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.42,0:00:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,About their lust, or their brutality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How they transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean intellectually.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never had any of it directed at-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.59,0:01:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he's a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a silent night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.71,0:01:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse was beginnin'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The overlapping moments
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.84,0:01:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We might believe them to be eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's darker than black
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The labyrinthine sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Begs for light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I bite your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The impulse eats away at me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... Can I... Can I... Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Libido erases my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Into darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have fallen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a hideous form
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If my human tears have dried
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you think of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NOur crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wets our bond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We share our weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NWe share our weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we two live on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Licking each other's wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Defining each other's life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirsting for love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chaser
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Inferiority complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you felt like you have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When devils date humans, they tend to be\Nmore conscious of how ugly they feel as devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not comfortable unless they\Nalways have a sedative on hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They subconsciously avoid\Ncommunication with non-devils
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually lose all faith in themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel like I am, maybe I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that young lady your girlfriend? She's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Too cute to let outside, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think you're being a little overprotective?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to put her in any danger, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's all, I don't know why you were\Nso scared the second she pushed back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you afraid of, Yuuki Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,scared of the devil inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't trust devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you like this guy,\Nall he likes is your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to give him my blood and it made him angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's progress.\NYou identified one of your problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been well aware of that problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew, but you didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really call that "well aware"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why do you think you're scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm a devil, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Kleemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the doctor who told me\Nto deal with bloodlust by jerking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NJust a- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From your attitude, I guess you ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you made it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,ONLO must be going nuts about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Tell me more about-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at him, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an example of someone\Nwho isn't afraid of his devil side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't worry about if he's a devil or a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like he was born with that attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing that makes it\Npossible for him to be so unconcerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He has learned to control the devil inside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They know this car's license number.\NI have to find another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You should see a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A hostage, worried about her kidnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing bothers you, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend of mine disobeyed orders to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They might kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They already did kill another one of our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Our leader has no mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't save him soon, it will be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you report them,\Nand get the police to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They never helped me before, and they won't now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I should drink blood and build up a tolerance like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinking blood isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Different things will work better for different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens to you when you transform?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What situations lead to a transformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to have exact answers to those questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So that you're not paralyzed with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagi told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you're so afraid of transforming\Nyou can't get anywhere near your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So first, you need to know yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if you want to\Nface your girlfriend and protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There are ways to train yourself\Nto control your bloodlust.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But to do it, you'll need her help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency message from B2 HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Target T, the suspect in the sniper case,\Nhas stolen a car and fled Shirase Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,taking a hostage with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The hostage is a young woman with short hair\Nand a scar across her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, we're here, Zero Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop myself from helping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I being too naive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Nine, were we followed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Just get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening to the police scanner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just what do you people do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This devil issue has been hidden for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mission is to expose it, warn people of\Nthe danger, and eradicate the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eradicate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you think you can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sit around and do nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils are supposed to be on standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you don't even know where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just wander around and hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The sniper. She's that girl with the rifle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she'd do anything to Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a reasonable person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yanagi said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That she didn't look like she was going to hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a woman who killed five devils!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's only killed devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't think of it as murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible she thinks of it as a kind of pest control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a devil. If you go,\NI think you'll only provoke her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you liked a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you fall in love with one of those monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not know what he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't start to like him\Nuntil after I found out he was a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you knew, how could you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You make this distinction between devils and humans,\Nbut they're basically the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that some can't handle blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The only visible difference is\Nthe dark circles under their eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and devils who drink blood don't even have those.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If they drink blood, the dark circles...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Public Security found the car you abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the GPS for both Zero Six and\NZero Five has gone offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned off our GPS trackers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:09:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this means that Zero Six and\NZero Five have been ordered to go after us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But both of them work in Public Security Division 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't have a lot of freedom to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I? You can't trust the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki, F Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The devils' bar Cross has been attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Two dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,B Squad's Sergeant Makimura had been\Nguarding the bar but is now missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying Makimura is the mole?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit. I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how many people are we dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we found the stolen car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two convenience stores nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Check their security footage\Nand see if you can find witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You call the cab companies and see if anyone\Npicked up any injured passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NYes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have people working inside\NPublic Security Division 5?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a civilian. The less you know the-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy I like is an officer in Division 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the man you shot the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was with him when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You're the one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Seven, it's Zero Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He attacked a bar in Ikebukuro and quit the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stick your nose into this any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in it pretty deep already. It's too late to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your boyfriend want you getting involved in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Police officers are trained and armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I'm armed, too, and I've had training.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But you haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think maybe, someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be something safer that you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikuhara, we identified the taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always wondering if there's\Nanything I can do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was told to just stay locked up inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated that, so I rebelled, and I went out anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When you like someone,\Nit's natural to want to be useful to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Know myself so I'm not paralyzed with fear, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do that, I'll need Tsukasa's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to put her in any danger.\NThat's why I'm trying to put distance between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She really isn't the least bit scared of me, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's never been scared of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd always look me right in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd never hesitate to do or say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I like about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why I must never, ever hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:12:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to protect her. And to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to rescue her, I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you came from ONLO.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean I can trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can trust you as a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I want to protect her,\Nthe less I feel like I can get near her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I transform, can I count on you\Nto keep her safe from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So that "I want to protect her" thing\Nis your excuse to keep avoiding her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you were from ONLO, so I thought\Nyou'd have some kind of a backbone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa is never afraid to confront you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you refuse to communicate with her.\NYou're all "I have to stay away from her."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you haven't even explained to her\Nwhy you won't get near her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about immature,\Nleaving out the important stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna keep spouting that\Nwishy-washy garbage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then maybe I'll take Tsukasa off your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Five? What are Zero Two's orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Seven, Nine, and the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take them all out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not going to be warm enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. To apologize for dragging you into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}If you have any trouble,\N{\an5}post a message here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They found the car ages ago,\Nbut I haven't heard any orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be giving orders over private channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We should move, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call the police, so you wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one thing you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out for Naoya Ushio. He's in Division 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He has wavy hair and a birthmark on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll probably be the first one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,His codename is Zero Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll let her have it, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think they're in room 902.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the police. Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When did the kidnapper leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A-a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry her out, Nanno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that's okay. I can walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do? That's Zero Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll go downstairs together, nice and slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check on the guys downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll split up, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Zero Five. Will she be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he has any reason to hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost our chance to get out.\NI'm guessing there are cops downstairs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your kidnappers. Did they say\Nwhere they're going, what they're after...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that Ushio from Division 5 is a spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There, it's all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The elevator's here! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The doors are closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually used a stun gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be enough to knock him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get away from him, and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I go downstairs, I'll run into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:16:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I never got Anzai's number.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know Sawazaki's, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Jill's, or Yanagi's, or Sakaki's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4}Search keyword
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4}Bar Sakaki
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Zero Seven, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You really want to wait on the roof\Nuntil the police leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we're not careful, we'll be like rats in a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop shouting. It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. This is so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'm stabbed in the stomach,\Nnow I'm getting shot at.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By humans who used to be on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought the devils were my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a human, but I'll be on your side\Nuntil the day I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna keep spouting that\Nwishy-washy garbage,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,then maybe I'll take Tsukasa off your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you babbling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lay a hand on her, and I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my guest. I'd like to see you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki, phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tsukasa, she called the bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai? I'm so glad I got through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In Tsukiji. A place called the Mino Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the sniper?\NI thought you were her hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But now someone else is after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The sniper warned me about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio in Public Security Division 5 is a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd run into him if I went downstairs,\Nso I came up to the higher floors...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see anywhere you think you can hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can get into room 1424.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll be right there. You hide in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm sorry, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I said a lot of things I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to be sorry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourteenth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The doors are closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just end this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time I saw her, I thought she was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,An innocent girl who would never have\Nanything to do with the underbelly of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so glad I found her\Nbefore she became his next victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I thinking of all this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you on your way as painlessly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why do you have to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm not ready to leave Division 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:19:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have you going around telling people\NI'm a spy for the CCC, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,CCC?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chosen Civil Community.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A fellowship of elect citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You call a group of murderers "chosen"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're killing people, but the name makes it\Nsound like that's the right thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's right or not is a separate issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have some kind of grudge against devils, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Actually, I like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel so sorry for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I work with devils on the force,\Nand when there's an injured human on the scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.92,0:19:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,they always look like they're in so much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They clench their fangs, fighting their bloodlust,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,begging for sedatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All the while, being treated like monsters\Nby the very people they saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Stay away from me, monster!\NAll the while, being treated like monsters\Nby the very people they saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but pity them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When I see a devil like that,\NI want to free them from their suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,From their cursed fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this Ushio guy looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't trust Division 5 anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to rescue her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I always end up putting you in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you care so much about them,\Nwhy are you trying to kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If they mean so much to you, shouldn't you try\Nto come up with a way to coexist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just your ego talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you live their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what they have to suffer through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that true for you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never lived a devil's life, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But you talk about freeing them,\Nlike you know what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You take their lives from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pretend to be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just looking down on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be begging for your life,\Nbut you're lecturing me instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes people angry, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Either you have nerves of steel,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,or you're just plain stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care which.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here is a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:22:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like softly melting away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could have loved each other more like that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What could I have told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.13,0:22:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A chance encounter that cannot amount to love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this filthy form is who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these fingers trembling as they touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of fighting together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hold you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect you without hurting you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You and only you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.80,0:22:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story of desiring forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Against the urges surging up inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, again, I..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep red dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we're softly melting away...
